884
01:16:46,382 --> 01:16:48,350
Fiquem todos do lado de fora.

885
01:17:50,379 --> 01:17:51,346
Victor.

886
01:18:03,325 --> 01:18:05,293
WILD BILL ARTIGOS DE COURO

887
